s the benefit of further alterations in lipid levels is anticipated to outweigh the potential risks.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/26638/', '', 'Perindopril, Indapamide, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, Colesevelam, Alirocumab, Fluvastatin', 'Fenofibric acid, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, Clofibrate, Fenofibrate, Bempedoic acid, Colesevelam, Alirocumab', 1767369485);
