ss the benefit of further alterations in lipid levels is anticipated to outweigh the potential risks.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/26701/', '', 'Rosuvastatin, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, Cholestyramine, Rosuvastatin, Colestipol, Colesevelam, Alirocumab', 'Fenofibrate, Bempedoic acid, Fenofibric acid, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, Clofibrate, Fenofibrate, Bempedoic acid, Colesevelam, More', 1767369485);
